---
/* Problem Section — "Le constat" with italic headline + icon cards */
---

<section
  id="constat"
  class="section-skew bg-surface-container overflow-hidden py-[var(--spacing-section-gap)]"
>
  <div class="section-skew-content">
    <div class="container-main">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-24 items-start">

        <!-- Left: Eyebrow + italic headline + body paragraphs -->
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow reveal">Le constat</span>

          <h2
            class="mt-8 font-display font-bold italic tracking-tight text-on-surface text-[length:var(--font-size-h1)] leading-[1.15] reveal delay-1"
          >
            L'ancien monde du freelancing meurt.
          </h2>

          <div class="mt-10 space-y-6 reveal delay-2">
            <p class="text-lg text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
              Pendant des ann&eacute;es, &ecirc;tre freelance signifiait vendre du temps contre de l'argent. Mais le march&eacute; a bascul&eacute;&nbsp;: l'IA et l'automation red&eacute;finissent ce que les clients attendent. Les comp&eacute;tences d'hier ne suffisent plus demain.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
              Ceux qui n'&eacute;voluent pas se retrouvent &agrave; courir apr&egrave;s des missions de moins en moins bien pay&eacute;es, face &agrave; une concurrence mondiale. Le mod&egrave;le du freelance g&eacute;n&eacute;raliste est en train de s'effondrer.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
              La question n'est plus <em>si</em> tu dois int&eacute;grer l'IA &mdash; mais <em>&agrave; quelle vitesse</em>.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: 2 icon cards -->
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-8">

          <!-- Card 1 -->
          <div class="p-8 bg-surface-container-high rounded-lg reveal delay-2">
            <div class="mb-5 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-tertiary/15">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-tertiary">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-on-surface normal-case tracking-normal leading-snug">
              Comp&eacute;tences obsolescentes
            </h4>
            <p class="mt-3 text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
              Tes clients attendent de l'IA et de l'automation, mais tu n'as ni la m&eacute;thode ni les outils pour r&eacute;pondre. Chaque mois qui passe creuse l'&eacute;cart.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Card 2 -->
          <div class="p-8 bg-surface-container-high rounded-lg reveal delay-3">
            <div class="mb-5 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-tertiary/15">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-tertiary">
                <line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="10"></line>
                <line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="4"></line>
                <line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="16"></line>
                <polyline points="3 7 7 3 11 7"></polyline>
                <line x1="7" y1="3" x2="7" y2="15" stroke-dasharray="2 2" opacity="0.5"></line>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-on-surface normal-case tracking-normal leading-snug">
              Course aux missions
            </h4>
            <p class="mt-3 text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
              Tu passes plus de temps &agrave; chercher des clients qu'&agrave; livrer des r&eacute;sultats. Sans sp&eacute;cialisation, tu te noies dans la concurrence et les tarifs baissent.
            </p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
